race.comment: NOAH'S BEST (1) has been hard to follow lately, running sixth (30.60) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at Warrnambool. Key player on best and worth another chance. MEAL TICKET (2) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (30.51) in a Grade 5 at The Meadows. Worth another chance. THEO'S DIM SIM (4) scored last time and can measure up again. Something for the Multiples: LEKTRA JANE (6)
